paper and then she turned

00:01:09.293 --> 00:01:11.634
them all upside down or
maybe she closed her eyes

00:01:11.634 --> 00:01:13.509
and then she moved them
all over her table.

00:01:13.509 --> 00:01:15.924
Then with her eyes closed
she randomly moved them to

00:01:15.924 --> 00:01:17.973
either the left or the right of the table.

00:01:17.973 --> 00:01:19.683
If they moved to the left
of the table then those are

00:01:19.683 --> 00:01:21.591
the days she'll take bus A,
